oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fort Pierce Bluegrass Festival in St. Lucie County (18229)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Flatt, Lester; Nashville Grass (Musical group); Osborne Brothers; Jim and Jesse; Martha White Foods; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Fort Pierce Bluegrass Festival with Lester Flatt and Nashville Grass, Osborne Brothers, Jim and Jessie and others at the St. Lucie County Fairgrounds on November 19-21. Poster features metal photoplates of Lester Flatt and the Nashville Grass, Osborne Brothers, and Jim and Jesse. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20987.
